==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Diphthongize
<hw>Diph"thong*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <def>To
change into a diphthong, as by affixing another vowel to a simple
vowel.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The <xex>diphthongized</xex> long vowels.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>H. Sweet.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Diphycercal</ent>⟦br⟧
